  29:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****                       ##### TIMER Extended features #####
  30:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   ==============================================================================
